N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 45.6 - Payment for outpatient and related medical care

State Regulations

Fees for outpatient and related medical care may not exceed those established pursuant to title 11 of article five (Medicaid) of the Social Services Law. Notes
